<center><i>Valas Defai, </i><a href=http://www.triadcontinuum.com/index.php><b>Triad Continuum</b></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukaziqueal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaziqueal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/3/01 11:34:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Manna Robe &amp; Epic combo</span><hr size=1> I only use my mana robe on long fights. I use it on yelinak while standing between casts. The refresh on db is just about = the cast time on the mana robe. Then when the ae goes off I run out and tick med for a bit. Yes tick medding is still very possible, the sit nerf didn't affect it at all.<br>
<br>
For those that don't understand what tick medding is I'll explain...<br>
Every 6 seconds the server checks to see if you are sitting down and updates your mana(a &quot;tick&quot;). If you are sitting when it checks, it will award you the bonus mana that you get for meditation. If you are standing, it won't give you the bonus mana. <br>
Now here is the part that most people don't know. It means nothing if you stand up between &quot;ticks&quot; because the server isn't paying attention to you until that 6 second tick happens. As long as you are sitting when the server checks it will reward you with the meditation bonus. So a wiz who wants to tick med his mana robe will watch for a mana update and immediately stand up and cast the mana robe. As soon as the robe casts he will sit and be in time for that server tick... rinse and repeat, the result is you get the extra mana from the robe as well as your meditation bonus. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=6648.topic&start=21&stop=21>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6734.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6787.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6648.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6648.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6648.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6648.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notificat